No. 10-731. David G. Walsh, et al., Petitioners v. Badger Catholic, Incorporated, et al. 562 U.S. 1280, 131 S. Ct. 1604,

179 L. Ed. 2d 517,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2058. March 7, 2011.

Motion of American Council on Education, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae out of time granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit denied.

Same case below, 620 F.3d 775.
